FBIS3-9574 "dreeu059_d_94006" FBIS-EEU-94-059 Document Type:Daily Report 23 Mar 1994 SLOVAKIA Results of March Poll on Electoral Preferences AU2503144494 Bratislava SME in Slovak 23 Mar 94 p 2 AU2503144494 Bratislava SME Language: Slovak Article Type:BFN [Article by "r": "The Movement for a Democratic Slovakia Would Be Voted for by 26.4 Percent; 10.8 Percent Would Not Go to the Polls at All"] [Text] Bratislava--Slovak Radio's Methodological Research Department carried out a public opinion survey from 11 to 16 March, in which 1,025 respondents over age 18 were asked the following question: If new parliamentary elections were to be held this week, for which party or movement would you opt? The results can be gleaned from the table below: ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Movement for a Democratic Slovakia |26.4| ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Party of the Democratic Left |11.0| ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Christian Democratic Movement |6.1| ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Association of Workers of Slovakia |4.8| ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Green Party |3.6| ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Coexistence |3.4| ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Democratic Party |3.3| ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Hungarian Christian Democratic Moveme-|2.2| |nt | | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Slovak National Party |2.1| ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Social Democratic Party |2.0| ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Party of Entrepreneurs and Tradesmen |1.5| ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Christian Social Union |1.4| ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |National Democratic Party |1.3| ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Alliance of Democrats of Slovakia |1.2| ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Communist Party |1.1| ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Farmers' Movement |0.8| ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Hungarian Civic Party |0.6| ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Agrarian Party of Slovakia |0.4| ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Other parties, movements |1.0| ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Do not know |9.6| ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Do not want to reply |5.5| ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Would not participate in elections |10.8| -------------------------------------------------------------------------------
